  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4500025">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4500025/" class="title-link">这个天国很八卦</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4500025"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2068224/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2068224/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">加里波第</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-03"
      class="main-meta">2010-12-03 15:01:55</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4500025_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读史的最大乐趣在哪里呢？一曰“以史为镜，可以知兴替”，说这话不是皇帝、历史学家就是装逼犯。对于平头老百姓来说，阅读历史可不是为了受教育，历史之于他们，就象是轻音乐、超女和意甲，是一种娱乐，说得更直白一些，是一种八卦。  自从文王演周易以来，八卦从来就是人民群...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4500025/#comments">(53回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">201有用 / 24没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4500025_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4500025_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5200071">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5200071/" class="title-link">不是天国的天国</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5200071"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/waterfire/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46649305-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/waterfire/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">丰子余</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-12-05"
      class="main-meta">2011-12-05 13:27:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5200071_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  　1.   　　   　　历史学在中国处于比较尴尬的地位，一方面想要研究真正的历史，另一方面又要满足统治者的政治需求。两相比较下来，服务于政治就成为第一标准，尊重史实则成为第二标准。这导致许多历史研究过于随意化，在评价与史实还原方面都有意无意地进行不定程度的重新编...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5200071_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5200071_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4534155">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4534155/" class="title-link">传统</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4534155"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zwrys/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1003510-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zwrys/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">飞行鱼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-18"
      class="main-meta">2010-12-18 16:27:45</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4534155_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  “有人赞有人骂的太平天国，到底是什么样子？” ——这句话好像很勾人哈，其实历史是什么样子的，在发生以后就谁也不晓得了。即便是不过150多年前的事情，的确让人不敢想象。不过，几十年前的事，都会被遗忘了，更何况150多年前呢？洪秀全天王真的像个传说。说不清楚的所谓历史...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4534155/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
